    <summary>Reads audio and video data from files, cameras, microphones, and generic media sources in Universal Store apps.</summary>
    <description>Reads audio/video data from files (StorageFile, IRandomAccessStream, path), cameras and microphone (MediaCapture), and generic sources (IMediaSource). Renders video samples to XAML's SwapChainPanel and SurfaceImageSource, rotates/converts them, saves them to JPEG. Universal Store apps targeting either Windows or Windows Phone are supported.</description>
